    "Therefore, the objective of this research is to explore the insights of ChatGPT in academia in terms of opportunities and challenges assisting students, teachers, and researchers.",
    "To attain this objective, data collected from different sources were analyzed following the noticing-collecting-thinking model.",
    "Then, the impacts of ChatGPT in academia were derived as opportunities and challenges.The significance of this study is that it aims to clarify the impacts of using ChatGPT and similar AI-based natural language models in learning environments.",
    "The purpose of the research is to significantly contribute to the state of knowledge on AI in education by investigating possible benefits, and concerns of this technology in educational contexts.",
    "Again, this study intends to fill a theoretical gap in the literature by focusing on the practical implications of ChatGPT in educational environments."
